<SPAN CLASS="comment">Old Sydney Town, Melbourne, July 2000.</SPAN><BR>
Sydney, Melbourne.<BR>
<table width="100%" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="log">
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;Old Sydney Town, playing with a <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/01ZoidLilCannon.jpg" target="new">'lil cannon</A>.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;..and a <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/02ZoidWhippingPost.jpg" target="new">whipping post</A>.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;..and being <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/03ZoidPrisonCell.jpg" target="new">imprisoned</A>.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;..and <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/04ZoidGallows.jpg" target="new">hanged</A>.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;..at <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/05OldSydneyTown.jpg" target="new">Old Sydney Town</A>, Gosford.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;On to Melbourne, and the <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/06PuffingBilly.jpg" target="new">Puffing Billy</A> railroad at Belgrave.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;The <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/07PuffingBillyEngine.jpg" target="new">engine</A> of the train, sat at Gembrook.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;The <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/08PuffingBillyatStation.jpg" target="new">train</A> itself sat at Gembrook.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;The <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/09GembrookStation.jpg" target="new">platform</A> at Gembrook station.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;A slightly more advanced <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/10FlindersStreetStation.jpg" target="new">railway station</A>, Flinders Street Station, Melbourne's first railway station. This station has the fourth longest platform in the world, incidentally.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;The <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/11ViewFromRialto.jpg" target="new">view</A> from atop the Rialto Towers, the tallest single-span concrete structure in the southern hemisphere.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;<A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/12CrownFromRialto.jpg" target="new">Crown Casino</A> as seen from the Rialto Towers.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;A sculpture of a <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/13RickettsSanctuaryDingo.jpg" target="new">dingo</A> amidst the rainforest at William Rickett's Sanctuary.<br>
<IMG SRC="ui/piccie.gif" WIDTH="14" HEIGHT="14" ALIGN="middle">&nbsp;Looking around <A HREF="Photos/SydneyMelbourneJuly2000/14RickettsSanctuaryGeneral.jpg" target="new">Rickett's Sanctuary</A>.<br>
